    "causal_summary": "The CLI orchestrator skills (`cli-opencode`, `cli-codex`, `cli-claude-code`, `cli-gemini`) drifted across five files. cli-opencode contradicts itself on subagent invocation (claims subagents are not directly invokable, then invokes them in references). cli-copilot's effort flag prose is inconsistent with the live CLI. The five prompt-templates files omit required model/effort/tier pins, embed `--yolo` write flags without approval gates, and miss explicit `--model` defaults.",
